items.title: Stock Radar: Narayana Hrudayalaya, Aegis Logistics, AGS Transact Tech, Tata Investment in focus on Muhurat Trading Day

items.title: Chartist Talks: Ashish Kyal picks these 2 buy ideas for Muhurat trading, believes Nifty can break August low in November
items.description: Poly Medicure has just given a breakout of the Rounding bottom pattern. Also, since October 28 not a single candle has given a close below previous day's low which suggests strength in trend.
